ekly: First Look at First Second's Spring 2018 Graphic Novels]</ref>\n**[[ANIMUS (graphic novel)|''ANIMUS'']] by [[Antoine Revoy]]\n** ''Chasma Knights'' by Kate Reed Petty and Boya Sun\n** ''One Day a Dot'' by Ian Lendler, Shelli Paroline, and Braden Lamb\n** ''Be Prepared'' by [[Vera Brosgol]]\n** ''[[Cucumber Quest|Cucumber Quest: The Melody Kingdom]]'' by Gigi D.G.\n** ''Science Comics: Rockets'' by Anne Drozd and Jerzy Drozd\n** ''Quirk\u2019s Quest: The Lost and the Found'' by Robert Christie and Deborah Lang\n** ''All Summer Long'' by [[Hope Larson]]\n** ''Pop'' by Jason Carter Eaton and Matt Rockefeller\n** ''Cottons: The Secret of the Wind'' by Jim Pascoe and Heidi Arnhold\n** ''Spill Zone: The Broken Vow'' by [[Scott Westerfeld]] and Alex Puvilland\n** ''[[The Dam Keeper#Graphic novels|The Dam Keeper: World Without Darkness]]'' by Robert Kondo and [[Daisuke Tsutsumi|Dice Tsutsumi]]\n** ''[[The Adventure Zone|The Adventure Zone: Here There Be Gerblins]]'' by [[Clint McElroy]], [[Griffin McElroy]], [[Justin McElroy]], [[Travis McElroy]], and Carey Pietsch\n** ''[[Delilah Dirk|Delilah Dirk and the Pillars of Hercules]]'' by Tony Cliff\n** ''Idle Days'' by Thomas D. Brousseau and Simon LeClerc\n** ''Science Comics: Trees'' by Andy Hirsch\n* Fall 2018<ref>{{cite web|title=Fall 2018 First Second Cover Reveal|url=http://firstsecondbooks.com/uncategorized/fall-2018-first-second-cover-reveal/|website=First Second Books|date=2018-01-08}}</ref>\n** ''Kitten Construction Company: Meet the House Kittens'' by John Patrick Green\n** ''Castle in the Stars: The Moon King'' by Alex Alice\n** ''The Creepy Case Files of Margo Maloo: The Monster Mall'' by [[Drew Weing]]\n** ''[[Check, Please! (webcomic)|Check, Please!: #Hockey]]'' by Ngozi Ukazu\n** ''Science Comics: Solar System'' by Rosemary Mosco and Jon Chad\n** ''Monk!'' by Youssef Daoudi\n** ''The Divided Earth'' by [[Faith Erin Hicks]]\n** ''On a Sunbeam'' by [[Tillie Walden]]\n** ''Secret Coders: Monsters & Modules'' b