ing. In April 1996, he was conferred the title Master of Chinese Folk Arts & Crafts by UNESCO. The city has a fascinating museum and exhibition of the art of the inside painter - many complex paintings done on the inside of small snuff bottles as well as special larger pieces of glassware.<ref>[http://www.xisan.com]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110207234337/http://xisan.com/ |date=2011-02-07 }}</ref>\n\nThere is a Buddhist Temple on the outskirts of the city which is well worth a visit, as is the bridge in the old part of the city - one of the few remnants of the old town.\n<gallery>\nFile:Hengshui_Old_Town_Bridge.JPG|Hengshui Old Town Bridge\nFile:Hengshui Buddhist Temple1.jpg|Hengshui Buddhist Temple\n</gallery>\n\n==Geography and environment==\n{{Weather box\n| width        = auto\n| metric first = yes\n| single line  = yes\n| location     = Hengshui (1981&ndash;2010)\n| Jan high C  =  3.2\n| Feb high C  =  7.2\n| Mar high C  = 13.7\n| Apr high C  = 21.8 \n| May high C  = 27.4 \n| Jun high C  = 31.9 \n| Jul high C  = 32.0 \n| Aug high C  = 30.5 \n| Sep high C  = 26.9 \n| Oct high C  = 21.0 \n| Nov high C  = 11.8 \n| Dec high C  =  4.9\n\n| Jan mean C  = \u22122.7 \n| Feb mean C  =  0.9 \n| Mar mean C  =  7.2 \n| Apr mean C  = 15.1 \n| May mean C  = 20.9 \n| Jun mean C  = 25.7 \n| Jul mean C  = 27.1 \n| Aug mean C  = 25.6 \n| Sep mean C  = 20.9 \n| Oct mean C  = 14.3 \n| Nov mean C  =  5.6 \n| Dec mean C  = \u22120.7\n\n| Jan low C  = \u22127.1 \n| Feb low C  = \u22123.9 \n| Mar low C  =  1.9 \n| Apr low C  =  9.2 \n| May low C  = 14.9 \n| Jun low C  = 20.0 \n| Jul low C  = 22.8 \n| Aug low C  = 21.5 \n| Sep low C  = 16.1 \n| Oct low C  =  9.2 \n| Nov low C  =  0.9 \n| Dec low C  = \u22124.8\n| precipitation colour  = green\n| Jan precipitation mm  =   2.0 \n| Feb precipitation mm  =   5.4 \n| Mar precipitation mm  =  11.4 \n| Apr precipitation mm  =  18.5 \n| May precipitation mm  =  37.4 \n| Jun precipitation mm  =  71.3 \n| Jul precipitation 